# Cost-mapping binary figures: regenerated from code + tracked CSVs, so they
# churn on every render even when results are unchanged. Keep them out of git;
# the CSVs (and the .tex table) are the diffable record of results. Force-add a
# figure (git add -f) only when its results have actually changed.
04_cost_mapping/output/*.png
04_cost_mapping/output/*.pdf
